"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/SLK-f3RAu-3a8vwQfzoAH.png?height=573&width=1198)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/ethersole/status/1463537481358491650](https://twitter.com/ethersole/status/1463537481358491650)\\n\\nDopex Buying & Staking 101 Chart with upwards trend\\n\\nThis thread will cover:\\n\\n* Buying $DPX\\n* Staking $DPX & $rDPX\\n* Compounding and Claiming those sweet rewards\\n\\n**\\\\*\\\\*This content may result in financial freedom and instant Chad syndrome so reader beware…**\\n\\nBest way to buy $DPX:\\n\\n* Get $ETH\\n* Bridge $ETH to Arbitrum via <https://bridge.arbitrum.io>\\n* Wait \\\\~10 mins for $ETH -> Arb network\\n* Head to <https://app.sushi.com/swap>\\n* Swap $ETH -> $DPX\\n* Sit back and realize you’re a chad now\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*This works for buying $rDPX as well\\n\\nHow to stake:\\n\\n* Head to the ‘Farms’ tab on the Dapp: <https://app.dopex.io/farms>\\n* Deposit into any of the 4 farms (pictured below)\\n* \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JiRp4q1ztPdaHDjqxkfRT.jfif?height=1668&width=3112)\\n\\nChoosing the best farm for you:\\n\\n\\\\- Single Side [$DPX](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24DPX&src=cashtag_click): Chad DPX bull\\n\\n\\\\- Single Side [$rDPX](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24rDPX&src=cashtag_click): Chad rDPX bull\\n\\n\\\\- DPX/ETH farm: Chad but still loves ETH\\n\\n\\\\- rDPX/ETH farm: Chad but still loves ETH\\n\\nIL isn’t a huge concern since these farms yield such juicy rewards.\\n\\nClaiming: On the same ‘Farms’ tab you will see a ‘Claim’ button show up after you stake your assets. In order to see accrued rewards you will click that ‘Claim’ button. How often you claim/compound rewards is up to you!! Always factor gas costs so they don’t eat into your ROI.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/96rFNAm0wNxDqNSsfjcm9.png?height=859&width=1569)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zsj8d9ARp2gnzdLew2i8W.png?height=899&width=1862)\\n\\n[https://app.dopex.io/farms](https://app.dopex.io/farms)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/3O5q32DL2YxZr63ZujDq7.png?height=915&width=1862)\\n\\nDopex通过期权池为期权交易方提供流动性，投资方包括量化投资机构Orthogonal Trading、Ledger Prime、Orca Traders、Pattern Research和SCC Investments等。\\n\\nDopex 是一个去中心化的期权协议，旨在最大限度地提高流动性，最大限度地减少期权作者的损失，并最大限度地提高期权买家的收益——所有这些都是以被动方式为流动性贡献参与者提供的。\",\"timestamp\":1641680559,\"title\":\"项目：Dopex\"},\"digest\":\"Y0a1GP6mNrXxq1HdSLx70kICIaHTtXCUilmkT9tobLk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd8E93E06a84581c10DC1F9F60ec91f0F38994f1b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aaVq_i5Hg2RcOkGUjwnNr1ZANbWWXGRh2_MDcWWBLkQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Vymj-lefhV15cwRTPjcA8PGQ3zwSpI_vYNEV2wT766c\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"sfxc641NrSPDa3QYag0HP87bZjEJKkxYnZDrScFlpaHAdJtgUdTdZ6tw3LmZRnA0Zg1wVgggT_QZnV7VCi1vuw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7ce1b5c537c8e4bc22897b790b18169a87b6f9aa0e9a9a7591e0573992e5956c7fb7939435ff8c64fd05e308f4dc38794d27ae953c8c31e7972f01b44a990bef1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aaVq_i5Hg2RcOkGUjwnNr1ZANbWWXGRh2_MDcWWBLkQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Vymj-lefhV15cwRTPjcA8PGQ3zwSpI_vYNEV2wT766c\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"BzitXWsxFel87ymVgybFPrM8aRpHDQ1mJjRS_-Xqn3g\"}"